from this $50 steak.

34:30.353 --> 34:31.976
It's all good... I'll take her home.

34:34.751 --> 34:36.500
See you tomorrow.

34:53.603 --> 34:56.705
I was surprised to get your text.

34:56.739 --> 34:58.540
You said I owe you.

34:58.575 --> 35:00.909
Actually, um, I owe you.

35:00.944 --> 35:02.344
How's that?

35:02.379 --> 35:06.148
Your speech was the lead story
on every statewide affiliate,

35:06.182 --> 35:09.243
and on the front page
of every local newspaper.

35:09.516 --> 35:13.102
And the governor is standing
right there next to you.

35:20.260 --> 35:21.779
Come on.

35:29.560 --> 35:30.506
<i>You're making me blush.</i>

35:30.540 --> 35:33.042
Really, under all that chocolate?

35:35.445 --> 35:38.947
You know he thinks we're
