35:38.982 --> 35:40.249
So why aren't we?

35:40.687 --> 35:43.976
Because if we do, I won't respect you.

35:45.055 --> 35:46.789
And I think I like you.

35:46.823 --> 35:49.191
Maybe I don't want
to be liked right now.

35:51.895 --> 35:53.629
Wow.

35:53.663 --> 35:55.464
Girl, you sexy as hell.

35:55.498 --> 35:57.332
But you've got some of the saddest eyes

35:57.367 --> 35:59.702
I've ever seen.

35:59.736 --> 36:03.866
I don't know, maybe
that's why I'm digging you.

36:04.741 --> 36:06.875
I appreciate the sentiment,

36:06.910 --> 36:11.013
but, um, you sound like
a real bitch right now.

36:15.018 --> 36:17.071
- Oh.
- Mm-hm.

36:44.981 --> 36:47.431
No, Shirlane, this is
not how things work.

36:47.541 --> 36:49.585
I don't give a damn about a heads up.

36:49.619 --> 36:50.986
That's too late.

36:51.011 --> 36:53.021
You're going to get me fired.

36:53.431 --> 36:55.457
When's it running?

36:56.693 --> 36:59.134
- What's going on?
- A video just hit.

36:59.159 --> 37:00.665
Of what?

37:00.690 --> 37:03.667
<i>But what is quite clear
are the racist remarks.</i>

37:03.692 --> 37:05.801
<i>Officials say those remarks
are from Joshua Beck,</i>

37:05.835 --> 37:08.237
<i>an African-American deputy.</i>

37:08.271 --> 37:09.805
<i>All right, fam.</i>

37:09.839 --> 37:11.740
<i>Just graduated from the Academy.</i>

37:11.775 --> 37:14.209
<i>Grown-ass man now. Any last words?</i>

37:14.244 --> 37:16.245
Uh, yeah.

37:16.279 --> 37:19.595
Um... finally got my license
to shoot these crackers.

37:19.620 --> 37:21.817
That's right, Josh.

37:21.851 --> 37:23.667
That's right, my boy's bulletproof.

37:23.692 --> 37:25.587
<i>Now, we've heard no comment
from Deputy Beck</i>

37:25.629 --> 37:27.081
<i>or the Gate Station Sheriff's Office</i>

37:27.106 --> 37:28.855
<i>regarding this inflammatory video.</i>

37:28.880 --> 37:29.747
Hello?

37:29.772 --> 37:32.278
<i>- Sources within the department say...
