38:25.019 --> 38:26.347
Sorry.

38:26.372 --> 38:27.438
Christian!

38:27.472 --> 38:29.021
There he goes.

38:31.977 --> 38:33.744
Look, it's not fair,

38:33.778 --> 38:35.813
but you're a distraction.

38:35.847 --> 38:37.481
