38:58.737 --> 39:00.337
The truth's easier to remember.

39:03.477 --> 39:04.720
Morning.

39:04.745 --> 39:06.492
- Have you seen the video?
- Not a good look.

39:06.517 --> 39:07.878
I've been in touch
with the governor's office.

39:07.912 --> 39:09.313
They want to know who leaked it.

39:09.347 --> 39:10.881
Me, too.

39:10.915 --> 39:12.116
I'll be ready in 20 minutes.

